Class Automaton<T>

java.lang.Object
  ie.ucd.clops.runtime.automaton.Automaton<T>
Type Parameters:
T - TODO
public class Automaton<T>
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a regular expression (command line format) as a finite-state automaton and enables traversing the automaton with tokens of the regular expression (options).

Author:
Viliam Holub, Mikolas Janota
